'''Sterilization spore probes''' were equipment carried aboard the [[inquisition module]] of a [[modular taskforce cruiser]]. Their main job was to be used for mass sterilization on a planet as a form of population control or even extermination. The Galactic Empire often used these devices extensively on small, rebellious planets.

